movie.title: Monkey Kingdom
movie.description_intro: A nature documentary that follows a newborn monkey and its mother as they struggle to survive within the competitive social hierarchy of the Temple Troop, a dynamic group of monkeys who live in ancient ruins found deep in the storied jungles of Sri Lanka.

movies.title: Pariah: The Lives and Deaths of Sonny Liston
movies.title_english: Pariah: The Lives and Deaths of Sonny Liston
movies.title_long: Pariah: The Lives and Deaths of Sonny Liston (2019)
movies.summary: Overcoming the seemingly insurmountable odds that life threw his way, Liston became the heavyweight champion of the world when he knocked out Floyd Patterson in 1962. Just eight years later, his wife finds him dead in their Las Vegas home from a supposed heroin overdose. Suspicion as to the cause of death pervaded among those that knew him.

movies.title: Gold Blooded
movies.summary: Dakota Fred Hurt, Dustin Hurt and the Richardson brothers battle nature, time, and death itself to strike gold under a huge waterfall. This epic documentary covers what Fred and Dustin were up to since they left the reality TV show that made them famous, and before their latest reality TV show.
